OL,3,COnline petition website would hold
OL,4,Cpoliticians to account, campaigners
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FCampaigners say the creation of a
OL,8,Fgovernment petitions website in
OL,9,FGuernsey would lead to more change on
OL,10,Fthe island.
OL,12,FCurrently, islanders who want to
OL,13,Fsubmit a petition must do so
OL,14,Fphysically to the States of Guernsey,
OL,15,Funlike the UK and Jersey, which have
OL,16,Fonline websites.
