OL,3,COnline petition website would hold
OL,4,Cpoliticians to account, campaigners
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FThousands of residents have signed
OL,8,Frecent petitions, including against
OL,9,Fthe introduction of GST, rising
OL,10,Fmooring fees and Guernsey
OL,11,FElectricity's 8% price hike.
OL,13,FHowever, none of these petitions led
OL,14,Fto a debate in the States.
OL,16,FMyles Duquemin, who organised a
OL,17,Fprotest and petition against the
OL,18,Felectricity price rise, says the
OL,19,Fisland would benefit from having a
OL,20,Fcentralised petitions system.
