OL,3,COnline petition website would hold
OL,4,Cpoliticians to account, campaigners
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FIt would also mean people could track
OL,8,Fand sign anonymously.
OL,10,FHe explains: "Putting it on a website
OL,11,Ffor everybody to see would make the
OL,12,Fgovernment actually think 'Oh, this is
OL,13,Fgaining traction; people need to do
OL,14,Fsomething', and I think they'd be more
OL,15,Finclined to do something."
OL,17,FNick Guillemette, President of the
OL,18,FGuernsey Boat Owners Association,
OL,19,Fhanded a physical petition to the
OL,20,FStates in protest against raising
OL,21,Fmooring fees.
