OL,3,COnline petition website would hold
OL,4,Cpoliticians to account, campaigners
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FMr Guillemette says having an official
OL,8,Fchannel for submitting petitions to
OL,9,Fthe States could encourage more
OL,10,Finformed decision-making.
OL,12,FHe says: "There's enough hot air
OL,13,Fspoken about in the States Chamber as
OL,14,Fit is.
OL,16,F"If we can give them some definite
OL,17,Ffacts to go on rather than hearsay or
OL,18,Ftheir own personal opinion, then
OL,19,Fobviously that does have a positive
OL,20,Feffect."
