OL,3,COnline petition website would hold
OL,4,Cpoliticians to account, campaigners
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FJersey already has a website where
OL,8,Fislanders can create and sign
OL,9,Fpetitions anonymously and force the
OL,10,FStates to respond to their concerns.
OL,12,FPetitions that receive 1,000
OL,13,Fsignatures will get a response from
OL,14,Fgovernment ministers, and any petition
OL,15,Fthat receives 5,000 signatures will be
OL,16,Fconsidered for debate in the States
OL,17,FAssembly.
