OL,3,COnline petition website would hold
OL,4,Cpoliticians to account, campaigners
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FHowever, since the website began in
OL,8,F2018, only seven of 604 petitions have
OL,9,Fbeen debated by politicians in the
OL,10,FStates, and only one has resulted in a
OL,11,Flaw change.
OL,13,FAny British citizen or UK resident can
OL,14,Fcreate or sign a petition in the UK,
OL,15,Fbut the petition must have at least
OL,16,Ffive supporters.
