OL,3,COnline petition website would hold
OL,4,Cpoliticians to account, campaigners
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FPetitions that reach 10,000 signatures
OL,8,Fwill get a response from the
OL,9,Fgovernment, and those with at least
OL,10,F100,000 are usually put forward for
OL,11,Fdebate in the House of Commons.
OL,13,FDeputy Sarah Hansmann-Rouxel,
OL,14,FPresident for the States' Assembly and
OL,15,FConstitution Committee, claims that in
OL,16,Fsome cases, Guernsey deals with
OL,17,Fpetitions better than other
OL,18,Fjurisdictions.
