OL,3,COnline petition website would hold
OL,4,Cpoliticians to account, campaigners
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FDeputy Hansmann-Rouxel claims: "In
OL,8,FGuernsey, you can email your deputy
OL,9,Fand phone them, so you have good
OL,10,Faccess already, which is what you
OL,11,Fwouldn't have in the UK necessarily.
OL,13,F"Also, within our assembly, we're all
OL,14,Fin government, which means any deputy
OL,15,Fcan bring forward a requete, which is
OL,16,Fa far more effective and substantial
OL,17,Fway of getting what you want."
