OL,7,FThe UK's Petitions Committee reviews
OL,8,Fpetitions published to find out more
OL,9,Fabout issues raised so it can push MPs
OL,10,Fto take action.
OL,12,FThe committee can also ask other
OL,13,Fparliamentary committees to look into
OL,14,Fthe topic raised by the petition.
